UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2446
1 AN ACT relating to legislative oversight.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 6.922 is amended to read as follows:
4 [Beginning in 2014 ]The Legislative Oversight and Investigations Committee of the
5 Kentucky General Assembly shall conduct an annual evaluation of the external child
6 fatality and near fatality review panel established pursuant to KRS 620.055 to monitor the
7 operations, procedures, and recommendations of the panel and shall report its findings to
8 the General Assembly.
